plot: It's board exams of Aman Mishra tomorrow and today is match between India and Pakistan at night and everyone is excited to watch it but there are other plans for Aman.

Annu organizes a cricket match screening at the Nagar Palika election candidate Prinsu's bungalow, hoping to get a gas agency license in return. Mishra Ji joins the gathering. Meanwhile, Aman despite being told to study for his board exams, decides to sneak into the screening.—ankurzden
